## Phase 1 — Spark Bootstrap

Goal: Spark generates the Phase 1 foundation — Vite config, theme, i18n, AnnouncerProvider, and the Layout shell.

**Spark Prompt**: Block 1 from `prompts/FINAL-SPARK-PROMPT.md`  
**Cost**: 4 premium Copilot requests  
**Expected Duration**: < 5 minutes generation time

| Deliverable | Acceptance Gate |
|-------------|----------------|
| `src/index.tsx` with **`GCThemeProvider`** (from `@eva/gc-design-system`) | AC-01 (no v8; no bare FluentProvider), AC-16 |
| `src/theme.ts` | GC design tokens wired; no hardcoded hex |
| `src/i18n/i18n.tsx` + both locale files | AC-03, AC-04, AC-05 |
| `src/components/Annoucement/` | AC-10 (live region present) |
| `src/pages/layout/Layout.tsx` | AC-06, AC-07, skip link, landmarks |

**Validation steps**:
1. Open Spark preview — no console errors
2. Tab through header — skip link appears, nav links reachable
3. Switch language — all strings flip, no reload
4. Open DevTools → Accessibility tree — `banner`, `main`, `nav`, `contentinfo` all present

---

## Phase 2 — Shared Components

Goal: all 20 shared components built and individually accessible.

**Spark Prompt**: Block 2 from `prompts/FINAL-SPARK-PROMPT.md`  
**Cost**: 4 premium Copilot requests  
**Expected Duration**: < 10 minutes generation time

Build order mirrors dependency graph. Components marked **`@eva`** must use the `EvaXxx` wrapper from `@eva/ui`; remaining components are EVA-JP-specific composites built on top of those wrappers.

```
AnnouncerProvider → WarningBanner → CharacterStreamer → UserChatMessage
→ Answer → QuestionInput (@eva: EvaInput, EvaButton)
→ AnalysisPanel → ChatHistory (@eva: EvaDrawer, EvaDataGrid)
→ ExampleList
→ FolderPicker → TagPicker (@eva: EvaSelect, EvaBadge)
→ FilePicker → FileStatus (@eva: EvaDataGrid, EvaBadge, EvaSpinner)
→ ResponseLengthButtonGroup → ChatModeButtonGroup (@eva: EvaButton)
→ RAIPanel (@eva: EvaDialog, EvaButton)
→ SupportingContent → SettingsIconButton (@eva: EvaIcon, EvaDialog)
→ Title/LoadTitle
```

**Component acceptance gates** (spot-check each):
- Focus ring visible on all interactive elements
- `role="radiogroup"` on all toggle groups
- Drawer close → focus returns to trigger
- `CharacterStreamer` has `aria-live="polite"` on its container

